_sText:
Map is dedicated to my server @ 173.199.80.58:27015

This is a medium sized arena, perfect for a fair sided Gungame. The many cars feature cover points, whilst a side path will take you on an alternate route to surprise your enemies.

The map is optimized as much as I could, rendered in 'fast' lighting without HDR for maximum FPS so that everyone can enjoy a great map with great detail and gameplay.
